{"tid":436754,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"發覺部分傑志球迷口出狂言","createTime":"2017-10-15T11:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T14:32:35.000Z","uid":44457,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"89ccf1f968eb2098ac5028344a473229c7157627","tid":436754,"uid":44457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"小傑仔，比你地今年拎到亞冠入場券又如何，咪俾你地戀棧多一年亞冠出局嘅歷史。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n何必笑我地司徒蛇呢。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講番今年聯賽，俾啲掌聲先啦！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中學陸運會指定動作 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天天天，你地聲震天。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n地地地，雖然你地有亞冠贏我地。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你地聲震天，你地聯賽排名又贏左我地。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我地實攞足總冠軍，我東冠軍必袋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n笑我地，又如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8e538319d6150185f8041d62378a3e5a9f18a8","tid":436754,"uid":44457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T12:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80d7238e49b3397ca666b230686870b97c418168","tid":436754,"uid":44457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:00:16.000Z","msg":"輕輕一堆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f258e2fa84ad8aae9137640c7267cf267d8802b2","tid":436754,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:03:22.000Z","msg":"上季都係東方多球迷入場<br />\n仲可以係旺角大農場扯紅旗"},{"pid":"69a2c0ccd369d355b38c5670536e848f3624c7a3","tid":436754,"uid":44457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T09:11:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上季都係東方多球迷入